sentences.english: Here are 18 of the world's strangest artificial islands.

sentences.english: Approximately 1000 dogs and cat live in Rokko Island.

sentences.english: Running out of coastline to build hotels?Build vast artificial islands with 120km of new beachfront.
sentences.chinese: 那就再建一個有120公里長新海岸線的巨大人工島。
